  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Collective rights management after Brexit
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">After Brexit, EEA collective management organisations may not automatically represent UK right holders and collective management organisations.</p>

  </div>
</div>

